npx create-react-app app-name --template redux

create firebase 

make firebase folder, copy over the config.

Move counter slice into the features folder
delete counter folder

Clean up the app.js folder

install react-router with 
    npx install react-router-dom

Follow React router documentation
https://reactrouter.com/web/guides/quick-start

Delete everything in app.css

In the index.css add:
* {
  margin: 0;
} 

in the body, add any variables such as colors.
--main-color: black; 
And
overflow: hidden; 

npm install @material-ui/core

npm install @material-ui/icons

install Styled components

styled-componenets.com/docs/basics

npm install styled-components

in package.json 

"resolutions": {
    "styled-components": "^5"
  }

Install redux
npm install @reduxjs/toolkit

